{"tid":1882993,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] 新GAME 熱練戰士 首抽建議睇回覆（4）","createTime":"2020-02-16T15:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:05:15.000Z","uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d62638329c56896718670a3c4ea25f717f847c4d","tid":1882993,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxsmTAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxsmTAi.jpg&h=716b3307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWrozP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWrozP.png&h=a5a127fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 邊到download?</span></strong><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%B4%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB/id1480645732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25A3%25AB%2Fid1480645732&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=fe10bbc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%B4%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB/id1480645732</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.superplanet.lucid2.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.superplanet.lucid2.global&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=11281342\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.superplanet.lucid2.global</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:隻game邊到黎，唔想再玩啲垃圾大陸game。</span></strong><br />\nA: 韓國GAME, 改編自同名韓國漫畫《熱練戰士》，係韓國公司SUPER PLANET出品，就算課金都唔會益到中共，好似係 (by 女人湯丸 &amp; 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 隻game點玩？</span></strong><br />\nA:隻game嘅戰鬥都係推圖為主 玩法有啲似epic7, king's raid個類<br />\n有pvp,但係打AI,唔係即時個種 (by 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:洗唔洗刷首抽？</span></strong><br />\nA:肯刷首抽嘅建議刷隻A+先開始,唔想刷嘅直接開始都好夠打 開波已經會送一隻A+筱蘿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XqD1TC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqD1TC0.png&h=53bf9eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:點刷首抽？</span></strong><br />\nA:完成教學之後佢會送2張卷(2抽) <br />\n+ 每日免費 (1抽)<br />\n+ 一開始送1000石 (300一抽等於3抽) Total 總共有6抽<br />\n抽完唔啱就可以去右上嘅 設定-&gt; 帳號初始化 再入數字就搞掂 (by 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:首抽邊隻最好？</span></strong><br />\nA:暫時都未有排行榜話邊隻最好，刷到A+基本上已經可以開波，A+係原生最稀有,比起A或以下嘅角色會多一項覺醒 = 多一招被動, 無論原生咩rank 都可以靠靈魂石升到上SS (by 百發百中)暫時比較多人讚嘅有: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/km0Ph3u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkm0Ph3u.png&h=ffb27e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金秘書 (高攻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FubnC3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFubnC3L.png&h=ec4b17a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萊茵 (神補，但你課夠50蚊美金會補底送一隻，唔諗住課嘅可以狗衝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKTYbo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKTYbo3.png&h=b0cb7b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海力阿契 (神坦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBrSfQW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBrSfQW.png&h=1e98ba84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱練戰士 (高攻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uz7x0hP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUz7x0hP.png&h=f51e3deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光明(勁，覺醒好撚型)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:普通券同高級券有乜分別？</span></strong><br />\nA:兩者都有機會出到A+ (by 老跋),但高級券個Pool應該少啲垃圾 好似係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:酒吧右下有個鑽石符號係咩黎？</span></strong><br />\nA:抽高級券/頂高召集唔招募再抽嘅話會比返30鑽你，如果見到A角都招募啦，因為可以開圖鑑有加成。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:我想入公會，有無連登公會？</span></strong><br />\nA:初初開始玩要等12個鐘頭之後先可以入公會，離開左舊公會之後都要等12個鐘頭冷卻後先可以入其他公會。<br />\n暫時連登公會有以下呢幾個:<br />\n貓巴士 (滿)<br />\n榮光光時<br />\nLihkg<br />\nStandwithHK<br />\n黃社團<br />\nDABINLO<br />\n香港人,黎明總會來<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:入工會有咩用？</span></strong><br />\nA:起營火比人參與同參與人地啲營火<br />\n起營火可以拎到30鑽，CD 4個鐘<br />\n參與人地營火可以加5體力，CD 1分半鐘<br />\n之後應該有公會討伐戰，但未開放<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">升等石(藍色)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">有乜用？</span></strong><br />\nA:將你人物升級，即係將你人物由A+升上S，由S升上SS。所有靈魂石都係共用，千祈唔好咁屎忽痕將啲B Grade升上去A (by 勞而不獲)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:升等石點攞？</span></strong><br />\nA:去酒館抽野，每次送你兩粒(by 路斯基7)或者商店都可以用唔同貨幣買<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">靈魂石(綠色)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">有乜用？</span></strong><br />\nA:可以提升技能等級，每一個人物都有自己嘅靈魂石，不可共用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:靈魂石點拎？</span></strong><br />\nA:抽到重複人物又招募左嘅會獲得靈魂石，20Lv去打靈魂石副本或者唔同商店都有得買。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:卡關點算？</span></strong><br />\nA:返返去之前啲關打支線或者重打刷裝，呢隻game啲裝備好重要，升左裝可以差成萬戰力，升裝唔貴盡量都升到+6，+6之後如果升級失敗就會-1。附魔都可以有效提升戰力，附魔券平時打都會跌，所以唔洗太過慳住慳住，刷啲啱嘅附魔對通關好有幫助。亦都可以睇下你嘅隊伍配搭，最常見都係1補1遠2近戰。[/quote]"},{"pid":"2f3590e361df33dc26bb8874b8426c4f1cf6c5e5","tid":1882993,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"小薯首抽建議 （by 行路草)<br />\n<br />\nA有神坦臨 如果無坦但有臨可以+1分<br />\n<br />\n無課:<br />\n雙A+ :<br />\n10分: T1 輸出 (雙技打全體) + 一隻t1 坦／補<br />\n9.5分: 雙T1 輸出/ t2輸出+ 補<br />\n8.5分： 1坦1補<br />\n(無課唔建議用喬 推圖相對比較慢)<br />\n<br />\n單a+:<br />\n8分： T1輸出 (巴打們首推金秘書)<br />\n7.5分： T1 補+ A英雙技輸出／ T1坦: （濃湯寶）<br />\n其他都唔建議了<br />\n<br />\n有課：<br />\n會課既 如果淨係想簡單過關<br />\n建議 臨+是但一隻t1輸出 就開<br />\n因為課50usd 有紅色t1補 其他可以睇返上面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTier list: by 路巴<br />\n坦：<br />\nT1 濃湯 T1.5 海力<br />\n推圖：<br />\nT1 金秘書 竹槍 T1.5 暗黑 金童 無名 <br />\n補：<br />\nT1 萊茵 韓秀雅 T1.5 羊男(因為男角)"},{"pid":"b4863e9e83cfabebbcd1ac041eb035ab9dbbde4f","tid":1882993,"uid":46611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"22f1add1e7212c8deaa06eb4cafbb6d02dacca7c","tid":1882993,"uid":22329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"06f6e1a4defcd446fa5f6ab6d5219aea12f2cfb0","tid":1882993,"uid":180069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:33:19.000Z","msg":"未入公會既, 可以考慮入黎<br />\n&quot;香港人，黎明總會來&quot;"},{"pid":"2dd349dcae95f44b293aab1ba2f137126ebd7656","tid":1882993,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"屌我又1001唔開POST我又開左個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8938b3f7200fcf15549002f2813d141d260b22","tid":1882993,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"推我呢個啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 齊哂所有野再置頂埋<br />\n最緊要係聽日好撚凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1882994/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1882994/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d78aa58bebc6720fcbb6c3ab4dca113cc5f5a4a9","tid":1882993,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:49:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申口口<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9HyrLW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9HyrLW.png&h=04140b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔計佢得一隻ss"},{"pid":"cc4050f9f547ff9831c1c3ec075684a60a542a2c","tid":1882993,"uid":33205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"靈魂石用黎升技定留返黎覺醒好?"},{"pid":"5be1947255e2dafa158114d3f005c759685de5a7","tid":1882993,"uid":22117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06f6e1a4defcd446fa5f6ab6d5219aea12f2cfb0","tid":1882993,"uid":180069,"l